---
title: Hearty Chicken Korma Curry with Spinach Rapid Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: There's nothing like mildly-spiced curry made with creamy coconut sauce for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the
fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious goodness!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
